---
title:  Nutty Chicken, Pear and Farro Salad with Goat Cheese and Maple-Rosemary Sweet Potatoes
description: This bountiful plate is not just another salad. Fresh pears and earthy, maple-rosemary roasted sweet potatoes add a touch of natural sweetness to complement the nutty farro. Goat cheese and toasted walnuts add textures that ensure this abundant salad is a weeknight winner.

Ingredients: Chicken breast • Sweet potato • Pear • Spinach • Farro (wheat) • Goat cheese (pasteurized goat's milk, cellulose powder, sea salt, potassium sorbate, bacterial culture, microbial enzyme) (milk) • Maple syrup • Walnuts • White wine vinegar (wine vinegar, potassium metabisulfite) (sulphites) • Whole grain mustard (water, white vinegar, mustard seeds, white wine vinegar, salt, sugar, mustard bran, citric acid, turmeric, spices, spice extract, natural flavour, xanthan gum) (mustard) • Parsley • Rosemary.
